
This program demonstrates how to calibrate a magnetometer
on the Raspberry Pi.
http://ozzmaker.com/compass3


The BerryIMUv1, BerryIMUv2 and BerryIMUv3 are supported.



To compile;
gcc -o compass_tutorial03 compass_tutorial03.c -lm
gcc -o compass_tutorial03_calibration compass_tutorial03_calibration.c 


More info here;
http://ozzmaker.com/compass3/
